			div.container
				center
					h1.indexHead3.zeroTop Websites done <span style='color:#43b04d;'> right </span>
				div.row.topBody
					div.span6.indexCaption3
						p.
							<span style='font-size:20px;color:#43b04d'> Why do I need a website? </span> <br/>
							<span style='font-weight:300'>
							In this day and age, the Internet is the new media king. In order to take full advantage of this 
							businesses are looking for websites that can clearly advertise their products while providing 
							customers with a convenient communication platform to use. We know this and we take many steps 
							to ensure that your website can do just that. 
							</span>
					div.span4.indexCaption3.whiteBox
						p <span style='font-size:20px;color:#43b04d'> Choose us if you want a site that is: </span>
						ul
							li <span style='font-size:13px;color:#43b04d'>&#x25BA;</span> Efficient
